{"id":2579,"date":"2024-12-10T16:53:58","date_gmt":"2024-12-10T16:53:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=2579"},"modified":"2024-12-10T16:53:58","modified_gmt":"2024-12-10T16:53:58","slug":"amulet-coin-upgrader","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/amulet-coin-upgrader\/","title":{"rendered":"Amulet Coin\/Luck Incense Upgrader (NPC)"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td><strong>Tehl Town<\/strong> &#8211; Standing in the center of Tehl Town near the statue.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Purpose<\/th>\n<td>Upgrades the player\u2019s Amulet Coin and Luck Incense in exchange for Big Nuggets<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Transaction Item<\/th>\n<td>Big Nuggets<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cost<\/th>\n<td>Depends on the Amulet Coin\u2019s level<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>The Amulet Coin Upgrade NPC is found directly south of the Tehl Town Pokemon Center.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/01-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-amulet-coin-upgrade-npc.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the Amulet Coin Upgrade NPC. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the Amulet Coin Upgrade NPC.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Purpose<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/12\/02-pokemon-unbound-upgrading-the-amulet-coin-for-big-nuggets.jpg\" alt=\"Upgrading the Amulet Coin for Big Nuggets. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Upgrading the Amulet Coin for Big Nuggets.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The first time you speak with the Amulet Coin Upgrade NPC he gives the <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-056\/\">\u201cStatue of Regi\u201d<\/a> side mission. Complete the mission and he\u2019ll upgrade your Amulet Coin to level 3 to ensure you get more money after each battle.<\/p>\n<p>You can then speak with the NPC again to further upgrade the Amulet Coin in exchange for Big Nuggets. <\/p>\n<div class=\"callout-box\"><strong>Note:<\/strong> While the NPC claims he only upgrades the Amulet Coin item, the Amulet Coin\u2019s level will match that of any Luck Incense you may have.<\/div>\n<p>The table below details all the Amulet Coin upgrades, including their cost and the increase in gained prize money.<\/p>\n<table class=\"table grey center\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Level<\/th>\n<th>Cost<\/th>\n<th>Prize Money Increase<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>3<\/td>\n<td>N\/A<\/td>\n<td>3x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4<\/td>\n<td>4 Big Nuggets<\/td>\n<td>4x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5<\/td>\n<td>5 Big Nuggets<\/td>\n<td>5x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6<\/td>\n<td>6 Big Nuggets<\/td>\n<td>6x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7<\/td>\n<td>7 Big Nuggets<\/td>\n<td>7x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8<\/td>\n<td>8 Big Nuggets<\/td>\n<td>8x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9<\/td>\n<td>9 Big Nuggets<\/td>\n<td>9x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<td>10 Big Nuggets<\/td>\n<td>10x<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"299\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Useful NPCs<\/strong>\n 